;; seed-capital-flow-graph.kotoba.edn — 潮目 (shionome) :representative seed (ADR-2606072200)
;;
;; HONESTY (G11): every record is :representative — illustrative public capital buckets and
;; bounded, rounded figures, NOT a live authoritative capture. Nodes are PUBLIC CAPITAL
;; BUCKETS (G1) — asset classes / sectors / regions / themes — never persons / accounts /
;; portfolios / individual investors. Edges are FACTUAL capital-flow OBSERVATIONS (G2, no
;; trade/advisory token), each :no-trade-notice true. Live full-universe ingest (exchange
;; data / fund-flow reports / central-bank releases / index providers) is G8-gated.
;;
;; THE DEFINING INVARIANT — トレードはしない: nothing here is a buy/sell signal, a price
;; target, or a portfolio call. The seed is shaped to exercise the analyzer: net flow per
;; bucket (where money goes/leaves), rotation pairs (どこからどこへ), inflow HHI, by-asset-
;; class + by-region slices, a risk-on/risk-off regime descriptor, and a correlation cluster.

{:graph {:name "shionome-capital-flow-v1" :visibility :public}

